23_28	0.0	The school's promotional material states the goal: ``Eventually, these highly-qualified public servants will themselves begin to run for elective office and will have the opportunity to lead our nation back to its constitutional roots''.
23_29	0.0	Those roots do not exclude religion, in Farris's view, and fundamentalist Christianity is clearly at the core of what the college hopes to stand for.
23_30	0.0	Students will attend daily chapel.
